text: Chynna Phillips (born February 12, 1968) is an American actress and singer who performed with Wilson Phillips. In the movie Some Kind of Wonderful, she played Mia. She played Mimi in Say Anything.... She is the daughter of The Mamas & the Papas band members Michelle and John Phillips.
